name: Lunch Hour, pre-Covid
description: Piece from a series of photographs of urban settings involving glass and metal surfaces, reflections and refractions. People walking beside a covered bus stop in a very busy spot on Paulista Avenue, São Paulo, Monday, September 01 2014. Coordinates: -23.558366, -46.659761. Originally released as HeN OBJKT 54233 on 29 April 2021.
